      "text": [
        " - سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْمَشْيِ مَعَ اَلْجَنَازَةِ فَقَالَ «بَيْنَ يَدَيْهَا وَ عَنْ يَمِينِهَا وَ عَنْ شِمَالِهَا وَ خَلْفِهَا."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.464 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from one of them (Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) or Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) ) that he asked about walking with the funeral procession.\nImam (as) replied: \"In front of it, on its right side, on its left side, and behind it.\""
        ]
      }
